Definition: mostly perennial herbs of northern hemisphere often with mat-forming habit
Example: most often placed in genus Arenaria: sandworts
Synonyms: genus_Minuartia, caryophylloid_dicot_genus, family_Caryophyllaceae, m, mostly, perennial, herbs, of, northern, hemisphere, often, with, mat-forming, habit, most, placed, in, genus, Arenaria, sandworts
Category: noun.plant
